Almond Butter Overnight Oats
https://www.purplecarrot.com/plant-based-recipes/almond-butter-overnight-oats-with-pear-pumpkin-seeds
Prep/cook Time: 5 min

2 cups gluten-free rolled oats
2 cups non-dairy milk (not included)
2 tbsp almond butter
2 tbsp maple syrup
1 tsp ground cinnamon
1 Bartlett pear, diced
1/4 cup pumpkin seeds

Combine oats, milk, almond butter, maple syrup, cinnamon, and a pinch of salt
in large bowl or container with lid. Stir well to mix in almond butter. Cover
and refrigerate oats overnight or for at least 8 hours.

Divide overnight oats between 4 serving dishes. Top with pear and pumpkin seeds.
